#inner-work[
  *The Ethics in Practice*

  Reflect on three years of engaging with others — within the TTAO community
  and outside it — about the Work. Where have you maintained the silence well?
  Where has the ego's desire for recognition caused you to share more than was
  appropriate, or in ways that were more about being seen as interesting than
  about serving the listener?

  Record honestly. Then write one sentence: what will you change in how you
  share the Work going forward?
